The global functional beverages market is witnessing substantial growth driven by consumer preferences for healthier beverage options. Probiotic drinks are gaining traction due to the increased awareness of gut health benefits. Energy drinks continue to be popular for their instant energy boost, especially among younger demographics. Fruit and vegetable juices, along with herbal and fruit teas, cater to health-conscious consumers seeking natural and functional beverages. Fortified water and rehydration solutions are preferred for their added vitamins and minerals, suitable for active individuals and athletes. Dairy and non-dairy beverages offer protein and essential nutrients, appealing to a broad consumer base looking for functional benefits.

